{
  "stem": "7600.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he had a toilet, one of these old-fashioned things with one of those big tanks, and you had to pull the string.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the whole house knew you went to the toilet because it made a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But that was-- I mean, this was supposed to be only for rich people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Ordinary middle class people, even though they were not bad off-- a lot of them lived in nice apartments-- they didn't have that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when I found that out, I thought it was-- And then also the people that I met.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now, I was brought up very formal because, in those days, everybody was formal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But Vienna, I thought, was ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I mean, every young man or older man, if you met a lady, he used to say, I'll kiss your hand, madam.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[GERMAN] That means, I kiss your hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he would actually kiss her hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was so formal that, let me explain something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Like, if you're-- if a woman was married to a doctor, she was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "If her husband was a general, she was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I mean, they were all with the titles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And some of them had ridiculously long titles that were ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were like in the 18th century, I thought.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They weren't living in the modern world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were so steeped in all of these things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I couldn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But that's the way it was in Vienna in those days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The city was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My cousin took me around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took me to the Burgtheater and the other theaters, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I met some of the people, I thought they were not as educated as the ones in Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
